<li style="text-align:justify;">China coronavirus death toll jumps despite lockdowns (DW, Germany),</li>
<li style="text-align:justify;">China instigates &#8216;unprecedented&#8217; lockdown (ABC, Australia),</li>
<li class="style-scope ytd-rich-grid-video-renderer" style="text-align:justify;">Coronavirus Is Worse Than You&#8217;ve Been Told (PeakP, USA).</li>
</ul>
